# Shaders

GLSL shader source files.

## Shaders to Create

- **glow.glsl** - Glow effect for bullets and engines
- **flash.glsl** - Flash effect for hit feedback
- **waveDistortion.glsl** - Wave distortion for special attacks
- **chromatic.glsl** - Chromatic aberration for impact

Ask @graphics to implement shaders and visual effects!
